column2: SELECT up_id, dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq(up_ra,up_dec,#) as objId FROM #upload WHERE dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq(up_ra,up_dec,#) IS NOT NULL EXEC spExecuteSQL &&&'&&&+ cast(x.objId as varchar(#)) + &&&&&& as objID, p.ra, p.dec, p.run, p.rerun, p.camcol, p.field, dbo.fPhotoTypeN(p.type) as type, p.petroMag_u, p.petroMag_g, p.petroMag_r, p.petroMag_i, p.petroMag_z, p.petroMagErr_u, p.petroMagErr_g, p.petroMagErr_r, p.petroMagErr_i, p.petroMagErr_z, p.extinction_u, extinction_g, extinction_r, extinction_i, extinction_z, p.dered_u, p.dered_g, p.dered_r, p.dered_i, p.dered_z, p.err_u, p.err_g, p.err_r, p.err_i, p.err_z, p.deVRad_r, p.deVRadErr_r FROM #upload u JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id JOIN PhotoPrimary p ON p.objID = x.objID ORDER BY x.up_id &&&#', @log=#, @filter=#
